Note: ============================================================================
Note: Fast Name-to-Number Lookup
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "get_linux_arm64_syscall_number" that takes name as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Returns the syscall number for a given syscall name on Linux ARM64
    Note: Uses direct string comparison for fast lookup without requiring a registry
    Note: Returns -1 if the syscall name is not recognized

    Note: --- File I/O ---
    If name is "read":
        Return SYS_ARM64_READ
    End If
    If name is "write":
        Return SYS_ARM64_WRITE
    End If
    If name is "openat":
        Return SYS_ARM64_OPENAT
    End If
    If name is "close":
        Return SYS_ARM64_CLOSE
    End If
    If name is "lseek":
        Return SYS_ARM64_LSEEK
    End If
    If name is "pread64":
        Return SYS_ARM64_PREAD64
    End If
    If name is "pwrite64":
        Return SYS_ARM64_PWRITE64
    End If
    If name is "readv":
        Return SYS_ARM64_READV
    End If
    If name is "writev":
        Return SYS_ARM64_WRITEV
    End If
    If name is "fstat":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FSTAT
    End If
    If name is "fstatat":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FSTATAT
    End If
    If name is "statx":
        Return SYS_ARM64_STATX
    End If
    If name is "ioctl":
        Return SYS_ARM64_IOCTL
    End If
    If name is "fcntl":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FCNTL
    End If
    If name is "dup":
        Return SYS_ARM64_DUP
    End If
    If name is "dup3":
        Return SYS_ARM64_DUP3
    End If
    If name is "pipe2":
        Return SYS_ARM64_PIPE2
    End If
    If name is "ftruncate":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FTRUNCATE
    End If
    If name is "fallocate":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FALLOCATE
    End If
    If name is "fsync":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FSYNC
    End If
    If name is "fdatasync":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FDATASYNC
    End If
    If name is "readlinkat":
        Return SYS_ARM64_READLINKAT
    End If
    If name is "faccessat":
        Return SYS_ARM64_FACCESSAT
    End If
    If name is "sendfile":
        Return SYS_ARM64_SENDFILE
